result.name: MeokBang Korean BBQ & Bar

reviews.text: I like to drink soju and get smashed.  Perfect place to do both, try not to pee urself tho.

Food was great, however the staff and management was very poor. Had to ask few times in order to refill the dishes, also took away the sauces from all of the table with no reason, had to ask them for more sauce but they just scooped some for us instead of putting back the jar onto our table. I feel like they don't want to let us use the sauce and refill the dishes as less as possible, lame.

Awesome location. Food is really authentic and we love the BBQ. I have been many times and I have always enjoyed my experience, comes highly recommended.

Would recommend the Hanwoo (it may be frozen but I found the cut to be more consistent, the octopus out of a few times we ordered are variable in size).

A very popular Korean bbq restaurant in town for new generation.
Price fare, food fresh, service good.
Open anytime in a day.
Reasonable price, relatively clean

result.name: 炑八韓烤

reviews.text:
這個韓式燒烤，一直想試卻未有機會，這裏座位很舒適，而服務也相當好，各式泡菜、烤盤邊的芝士粟米及泡菜煎蛋，是免費供應並可免費添食。

食物品質很不錯，味道也很好，以這價格來說是不錯，只是略嫌冷氣不夠，可能是我坐的位置有關題吧！

晚餐好貴，一份牛小排得8件要$190。個鐵板上面成浸油，燒乜都燶又”痴”底。食物又冇味。
我兩個仔食完仲肚痾，以後都唔會再去😡
三人入座其中一人是五歲小童，安排坐圓凳座位，要求坐卡位，(小童不會向後跌，安全些)女侍應竟說卡位已被訂枱，😱😱午餐時間八人以上才需訂枱呀!!!新來的侍應還是說謊的侍應？請問一個卡位如何能坐八人？
星期五~日只有90分鐘，入座又無説明，最后有點忙，還好夠鐘未有崔客，食物都ok。
I like to drink soju and get smashed.  Perfect place to do both, try not to pee urself tho.
